title: Sheex Performance Sheet Set
transcripts:
Female: I am my own personal trainer. In the boardroom, the classroom, the weight room. And for me to compete, I have to sleep. Because the best way to have it all is to wake up ready.

Male: Introducing Sheex Performance Sheets with Sleep Fit technology.

Male: Sheex keeps me at the right temperature, which helps me sleep better and play better.

Female: I'm a tactile person. It's just the feel of them. They're so soft.

Male: I'm not hot, I'm cool, and I can sleep really well with these Sheex.

Female: They're so soft and comfortable and help me rejuvenate for the next day.

Male: By keeping you comfortable but never too warm, Sheex create the optimal temperature for sleep.

Male: When you're trying to cool yourself, you sweat and you need to get rid of the sweat. Sheets that allow the moisture to really be wicked away from the body would be very, very helpful.

Female: As athletes and coaches, we know the importance of staying dry and cool. As it turns out, the same is true for quality sleep.

Male: Sheex are unique in that they're made out of performance fabrics that slowly release sleep-disrupting heat and wick moisture away from your skin, helping provide the best temperature for a deep, relaxing sleep. Sheex breathe nearly 50 percent better than cotton, release twice as much heat as traditional bedding, have three times the drying power of cotton, and contain Lycra for freedom of movement all night long. Giving you a better night's sleep.

Male: Are you ready to wake up ready? Then take your sleep and your life to the next level with Sheex Performance Sheets. Sleep better, live better. Sheex.
